      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "docker run can also connect host users's terminal with STDIO streams of the containerised application\nvia docker cli by instructing it with right flags ",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "docker run can also connect host users's terminal with STDIO streams of the containerised application\nvia docker cli by instructing it with right flags ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
